  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\n        \n\n    \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe could never understand \u003ca href=\"https://cheezburger.com/37510917/i-will-absolutely-not-be-getting-rid-of-my-cat-person-refuses-to-abandon-their-cat-after-their\"\u003epeople who abandon their cats\u003c/a\u003e. Sure, sometimes, cats and people don\u0026#39;t get along, and maybe yours is not the house this kitty was meant to be in. But to abandon it? On the street? Alone? Unacceptable. There are so many other solutions. You could \u003ca href=\"https://cheezburger.com/19206917/meet-the-newly-adopted-faces-of-the-week\"\u003efind the cat a new family\u003c/a\u003e, or you could bring it to a shelter. Anything except leaving it in a carrier outside - confused, alone and terrified - and hoping that someone will just pop up and pick them up.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSadly, that\u0026#39;s exactly what happened in today\u0026#39;s story. This adorable cat was abandoned by its previous owners. It is sheer luck - or maybe the Cat Distribution System performed some of its magic - that sent these \u003ca href=\"https://cheezburger.com/36872965/i-had-to-save-her-person-adopts-a-senior-cat-that-had-been-hit-by-a-car-after-five-weeks-of\"\u003ewonderful people to save this cat\u003c/a\u003e. As angry as we are about the people who abandoned this precious kitty, we are a million times more thankful to the ones who rescued it and worked so hard and for so long to gain its trust.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10423772672/h082F1605/up-seemed-be-an-abandoned-pet-on-hot-august-day-and-he-hated-months-he-just-let-pet-him-first-time\" id=\"_r_a_10423772672\" width=\"715\" height=\"419\" alt=\"r/cats 1 day ago Imaotorii picked up what seemed to be an abandoned pet on a hot August day and he hated me for months. He just let me pet him for the first time.\" title=\"\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eFirst of all, the people who abandoned him should be ashamed. No note, no nothing, just leaving the poor thing out there in the world in its carrier, hoping that what- someone would pick him up? It\u0026#39;s a miracle that someone did, and that they are as kind as they are. \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10423776512/h668C91E5/food-but-wont-even-eat-just-keeps-meowing-this-poor-soul-is-anyone-able-help-or-pick-this-baby-up\" id=\"_r_a_10423776512\" width=\"800\" height=\"1013\" alt=\"groceries and I saw a beautiful blue eyes cat in its carrier off to the side. Someone just left it. I went and bought food but it won\u0026#39;t even eat. Just keeps meowing. This poor soul. Is anyone able to help or pick this baby up?\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eAnd second of all, months is nothing in this situation. Cats whose trust in humans has been so painfully broken could take years to warm up to someone. It\u0026#39;s a testament to how sweet the cat is and how great his new owners are that it happened this quickly. \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10423787008/hA4EBA8E3\" id=\"_r_a_10423787008\" width=\"709\" height=\"950\" alt=\"Cheezburger Image 10423787008\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10423772928/h76335B5F/either-way-glad-been-able-take-good-care-him-and-hes-warming-up-poor-kitty-congrats-on-hard-work\" id=\"_r_a_10423772928\" width=\"671\" height=\"306\" alt=\"rockthrowing • 1d ago • Did you see if he was chipped?? It\u0026#39;s possible he was the victim/collateral damage of a DV situation. It\u0026#39;s not uncommon for the abuser to dump a beloved pet like this as punishment. Either way, I\u0026#39;m glad you\u0026#39;ve been able to take good care of him and he\u0026#39;s warming up to you. Poor kitty. Congrats on your hard work!!!\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e5\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10423772416/hE774CC67/didnt-know-anyone-with-personal-scanner-so-now-he-is-little-more-friendly-will-get-him-scanned-asap\" id=\"_r_a_10423772416\" width=\"608\" height=\"262\" alt=\"Imaotorii OP • 23h ago • We were never able to to touch him or come close to him at all once we got him out of his carrier. He was very aggressive and we didn\u0026#39;t know anyone with a personal scanner so now that he is a little more friendly we will get him scanned asap\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e6\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10423772160/hB05B1FFF/little-pj-1d-ago-this-is-so-sweet-also-is-just-or-does-this-cat-seem-huge-loll\" id=\"_r_a_10423772160\" width=\"664\" height=\"159\" alt=\"• little-pj 1d ago • this is so sweet!!! also is it just me or does this cat seem HUGE loll\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e7\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10423773440/hA10A0F13/imaotorii-op-23h-ago-yes-he-massive-originally-but-he-has-lost-few-lbs-since-lol\" id=\"_r_a_10423773440\" width=\"615\" height=\"155\" alt=\"Imaotorii OP • 23h ago • Yes he was MASSIVE originally but he has lost a few lbs since lol\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10423773184/h0A3F6B23/tomuch-funallegedly-1d-ago-is-he-cross-eyed-or-is-just-picture-because-love-so-much-either-way\" id=\"_r_a_10423773184\" width=\"674\" height=\"162\" alt=\"ToMuch FunAllegedly 1d ago • Is he cross eyed or is that just the picture because I love it so much either way..\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e9\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10423773696/hD44F2B82/op-23h-ago-have-noticed-his-eyes-tremor-and-he-is-definitely-cross-eyed-lol-getting-him-vet-asap\" id=\"_r_a_10423773696\" width=\"622\" height=\"159\" alt=\"Imaotorii OP • 23h ago • We have noticed his eyes tremor and he is definitely cross eyed lol. Getting him to the vet asap\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10423773952/hEA848A93/and-now-he-doesnt-ever-bite-scratch-or-anything-bad-and-just-wants-affection-and-show-off-21k-reply\" id=\"_r_a_10423773952\" width=\"665\" height=\"311\" alt=\"fallenredwoods • 1d ago. Good on you OP. I swear, the bigger the a hole a cat is the bigger the lover they eventually become. My cat had to be pet with leather gloves because he was feral and now he doesn\u0026#39;t ever bite, scratch or anything bad and just wants affection and to show off 2.1K \u0026gt; Reply\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e11\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e