-do-08-so-glad-took-him-and-hes-warming-up-keep-giving-him-all-love-and-care-op\" id=\"_r_a_10423774720\" width=\"633\" height=\"292\" alt=\"Ms_Anonymous123 1d ago Edited 1d ago • Tabbycat Ugh that\u0026#39;s awful. How could someone just do that 08 So glad you took him in and he\u0026#39;s warming up to you Keep giving him all the love and care OP\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e14\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10423775232/hD04A62CE/with-being-abandon-by-its-original-owner-and-has-accepted-now-as-its-owner-poor-kitty-u-rock-op\" id=\"_r_a_10423775232\" width=\"664\" height=\"192\" alt=\"00 shuntman2 • 1d ago • It probably only just came to terms with being abandon by its original owner and has accepted you now as its owner poor kitty u rock OP\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e15\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10423774976/h86ADAE9B/pos-owner-left-cat-with-carrier-sealed-wasnt-sealed-right-theyre-evil-either-way-regardless-though\" id=\"_r_a_10423774976\" width=\"665\" height=\"199\" alt=\"Mia_Magic 1d ago • Void Don\u0026#39;t tell me the POS owner left the cat with the carrier sealed. It wasn\u0026#39;t sealed right? They\u0026#39;re evil either way regardless though\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\